		</div>
	</div>
</div>Grinding in WoW is nothing like grinding in EQ. WoW is the same &quot;content&quot; reskinned and passed off as fresh every expansion aka daily quests.  EQ was always about other people, unless you were a cool kid and could solo.  WoW is a really shitty single player game.  EQ was political warfare with deep social networks, and its game mechanics were sufficiently open ended to allow for things like quad kiting and pulling entire zones for slaughter by 5 very precise people.  If you had skill and creativity anything was possible, such as that guy who solo'd the Plane of Hate back in the day despite the mobs being faster than him even w/ SoW (iirc) or Fansy trolling an entire server by being under level 5.
